{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9b2d7bbfb7","title":"关于收集和研究上海税收办法的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f402bc5b58","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":4,"articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"fe158be820","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"海一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任。"},{"id":"969a6143be","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共上海市委在1949年11月1日给中央的电报中转述的英国侨民致英政府备忘录要点。转述的要点有：“英侨情况，现亦略好转。对身受政府一视同仁之待遇，无不感激。惟对某些税收制度及劳资问题，尚有意见。例如，税收方法、税率及制度，全国应一致。在天津之合并征收所得税及营业税，似非合理，更依照“付税能力”强定工商业税，亦不科学，对工商业均有严重不良影响。惟上海之营业税法及印花税法，系参动本市实际情况而定，人民无不称善。"},{"id":"31202ddba1","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄敬，当时任中共天津市委书记、天津市人民政府市长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"0e69ca15dd","type":"title","text":"关于收集和研究上海税收办法的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7"},{"id":"fe158be820","type":"paragraph","text":"薄一波\"同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7"},{"id":"969a6143be","type":"paragraph","text":"请将此项情报抄送黄敬，并收集上海税收办法，加以研究","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7"},{"id":"31202ddba1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7"},{"id":"346d1d00f7","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7"}],"page":{"id":"da6153cd67","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"9b2d7bbfb7","